article.description: — Noah Van Bibber had 22 points in Winthrop's 89-51 victory over Holy Cross on Friday night.
article.headline: Van Bibber scores 22, Winthrop secures 89-51 victory over Holy Cross
article.linkText: Van Bibber scores 22, Winthrop secures 89-51 victory over Holy Cross
article.story: ROCK HILL, S.C. -- — Noah Van Bibber had 22 points in Winthrop's 89-51 victory over Holy Cross on Friday night. Van Bibber was 6 of 9 shooting, including 6 for 8 from 3-point range for the Eagles (2-2). KJ Doucet scored 15 points and Nick Johnson added 14. Caleb Kenney led the way for the Crusaders (1-3) with 11 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
